		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#010101"><strong>LEADER AND MENTOR ROLES</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222"><p>We have a number of diverse and challenging roles available on our seasonal programmes, from leadership and mentoring to skill-sharing and logistical roles.</p>
		
		<p><strong><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities"_blank">Leadership roles:</a></strong> Lead between 60-84 young people and 15 staff members through a complex and demanding programme as a <strong>Programme Leader (PL)</strong>, or support the PL and take on responsibility for managing challenging behaviour as an <strong>Assistant Programme Leader (APL)</strong>. Click on the link above to learn about our other leader/management roles!</p>
		
		<p><strong><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities"_blank">Mentor roles:</a></strong> Facilitate, lead and pastorally care for your team, assisting in their personal development as a <strong>Senior Mentor (SM)</strong>, or take a lead on delivering the NCS curriculum and social action projects as a <strong>Senior Community Facilitator (SCF)</strong>.</p></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
