		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222"><p><strong><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities"_blank">Practitioner roles:</a></strong> (Non-residential) Use your drama, media, enterprise, photography, music, art or sport expertise to deliver skill-building workshops, and help your team to use this skill to interact with their community.</p>
		
		<p><strong><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities"_blank">Inclusion roles:</a></strong> (Semi-residential) Work closely with a young person with additional or behavioural needs, ensuring that they participate to their full potential and helping them to intergrate with the rest of the team. Find out more about our new inclusion roles in the link above!</p>


		<p><strong>Many of our roles have a residential element to them. Please check individual role descriptions on <a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/seasonal-roles" target="_blank">www.ncsthechallenge.org/seasonal-roles</a></strong></p>

		
		<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HipmFuhICtQ&feature=youtu.be" target="_blank"><img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016_staffing_video_print_screen.JPG" alt="Click to watch full clip" width="550" height="450" border="0" style="display:block"></a></p></td>
		
